# Decide tooling on managing diagrams
 - __status:__       Decided
 - __Last updated:__ 25/02/2023
 - __Objective:__    

## Context and problem statement
---
Need an automation solution that performs IAC while enables checking external conditions such as git branches and user status



---
## Priorities & Constraints
- Provides IAC
- Supports scripting and conditions/loops
- Support GCP
---
## Considered Options
 1. Terraform
 2. Puppet
 3. Ansible
 4. Pulumi
 5. Jenkins

---
## Decision
---
Pulumi meets all requirements

## Expected consequences
The infrastructure will be managed with Pulumi, language to manage Infrastructure will be YAML/Javascript or Python.